PrecisOrder designating the following four railway stations as "HERITAGE RAILWAY STATIONS" for the purposes of this Act. 1. Union Station (CPR), Thunder Bay, Ontario 2. CPR Station, Kenora, Ontario 3. White Pass and Yukon Railway Station, Carcross, Yukon Territory 4. CNR Station, Richmond, Quebec.
